                    <ul class="my-4">
                        <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> One-time & Recurring Rides</li>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Real-time Seat Tracking</li>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i> Automatic Ride Matching</li>
